metadata.name: Same, Same But Different
metadata.description:
She was in the room, but somehow everything changed. Beyond the window - which was now located on the floor - the starry sky was shining, surrounded by countless monitors with flowers growing through their screens and swarms of butterflies flying everywhere... Avril for some reason was floating in the middle of the room with her teddy bear, which she was desperately trying to catch.
"What the hell is going on here?" - she thought to herself.
